an, save, schedule, list, run, and archive reusable prompts/workflows across desktop and Lark. actions=read,create,update,delete,execute\n- search-zoho-context: Search indexed Zoho CRM records (deals, contacts, tickets) from the vector database. actions=read\n- read-zoho-records: Fetch formatted Zoho CRM data with risk analysis, health reports, and pipeline summaries. actions=read\n- zoho-agent: Delegate to the Zoho CRM specialist agent for deep CRM data queries. actions=read,create,update,delete\n- zoho-write: Create, update, and delete Zoho CRM records, notes, and attachments after human approval. actions=create,update,delete\n- zoho-books-read: Read Zoho Books finance records, contacts, vendor payments, bank accounts, credit notes, sales orders, purchase orders, bank transaction match suggestions, and related invoice/email/statement/document metadata. actions=read\n- zoho-books-write: Create, update, delete, reconcile, categorize, email, remind, import, and status-change Zoho Books records after human approval. actions=create,update,delete,send\n- zoho-books-agent: Delegate to the Zoho Books specialist workflow for finance operations. actions=read,create,update,delete,send\n- read-outreach-publishers: Fetch outreach publisher inventory using structured filters such as client URL, DA/DR, country, and pricing. actions=read\n- outreach-agent: Delegate to the outreach specialist agent for publisher filtering and SEO inventory queries. actions=read\n- search-agent: Delegate to the research agent for external web research and exact-site page context. actions=read\n- search-read: Search the web via Serper, then fetch result pages to extract page context. actions=read\n- context-search: Search personal conversation history, uploaded documents, and Zoho CRM context through one unified retrieval interface. actions=read\n- lark-base-read: List records from Lark Base / Bitable tables. actions=read\n- lark-base-write: Create or update records in Lark Base / Bitable tables. ac